      "text": [
        " تُدْفَنُ الْمَرْأَةُ إِلَى وَسَطِهَا ثُمَّ يَرْمِي الْإِمَامُ ثُمَّ يَرْمِي النَّاسُ بِأَحْجَارٍ صِغَارٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Usman Bin Isa, from Sama’at Bin Mahran, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The woman is buried up to her waist, then the Imam<sup>asws</sup> pelts, then the people pelt, with the small stones’."
        ]
      }
